Description.TranslatedText: Terminology relevant to the test names that describe pharmacogenomics findings.

EnumeratedItem.nciodm:CDISCDefinition: Mutually exclusive alternative forms of the same gene occupying the same locus on homologous chromosomes, differing in nucleotide sequence and governing the same biochemical and developmental process. (NCI)
